Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.x509

Class PolicyQualifierInfo

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.x509.PolicyQualifierInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
ASN1Encodable, Encodable
public class PolicyQualifierInfo
extends ASN1Object
Policy qualifiers, used in the X509V3 CertificatePolicies extension. 
   PolicyQualifierInfo ::= SEQUENCE {
       policyQualifierId  PolicyQualifierId,
       qualifier          ANY DEFINED BY policyQualifierId }

  PolicyQualifierId ::= OBJECT IDENTIFIER ( id-qt-cps | id-qt-unotice )
